{
  "stem": "6195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my father said to him, never, ever would I imagine that the nation that produced [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Schiller and, and, Beethoven and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all the great people, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] could do something like that.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's absolutely inhuman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, I have to not only agree with you, but I want you to understand my pain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have a son in the SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want to know him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't want to see him, and I don't want-- I hope he never comes back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when he left, I made a cup of tea for him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If he-- even if he would, I, I wouldn't have remembered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he talked to my father, and my father was very knowledgeable in German literature.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and they talked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father's nose was, was running with blood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I begged my father to keep his head back and the cold sponge on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyhow, he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, I'm just as disgusted with the regime as you are.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, why-- how come you trust us and you are telling us all about it?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One has to talk to someone sometimes, he said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then next day, in the morning, we were told all the silver-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all the tenants', not only us-- not the Christians, the Jews-- all the silver to be taken down to the-- on the truck.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Actually, I started going out with the pieces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my parents had an enormous amount of antique silver and such silver, other silver.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You had to have for Pesach.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
